addTransactionEntry(uint256[28],uint256,.details: Function to add a new transaction entry.

params._features: Array of 28 uint256 values representing features V1 to V28.
params._timestamp: Timestamp representing the time of the transaction.
params._transactionClass: Class of the transaction (0 for Legitimate Transaction, 1 for Fraud Transaction).

editTransactionEntry(uint256,uint256[28].details: Function to edit an existing transaction entry.

params._features: Array of 28 uint256 values representing features V1 to V28.
params._timestamp: Timestamp representing the time of the transaction.
params._transactionClass: Class of the transaction (0 for Legitimate Transaction, 1 for Fraud Transaction).
params._transactionId: ID of the transaction entry to be edited.

getTransactionEntry(uint256).details: Function to fetch details of a transaction entry by ID.

params._transactionId: ID of the transaction entry to fetch.

getTransactionEntry(uint256).return: features Array of 28 uint256 values representing features V1 to V28.timestamp Timestamp representing the time of the transaction.amount Amount of the transaction.transactionClass Class of the transaction (0 for Legitimate Transaction, 1 for Fraud Transaction).
